---
title: Falafel and Chicken Couscous with Blistered Tomatoes, Olives and Feta
description: We're celebrating Mediterranean flavours with this Middle Eastern-inspired couscous! Packed with oven-roasted falafel, succulent chicken, blistered tomatoes, briny olives, feta and garlic-tossed carrots, this dish has checked off every flavour box!
